'''Installation'''<br />
Use Qubes Q3.

'''1. Launch dom0 Terminal'''
<code>
Qubes App Launcher (blue/grey "Q")
</code>

[[File:qubes-whonix1.png]]

Then go to:- 
<code>
System Tools -> Konsole
</code>

'''2. Install Whonix-Gateway and Whonix-Workstation TemplateVM'''

Write down this command inside the konsole , then hit "Enter". 

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo qubes-dom0-update --enablerepo=qubes-templates-community qubes-template-whonix-gw qubes-template-whonix-ws
}}

'''3. Make sure inactive VMs are shown'''

In Qubes VM manager, if you do not see {{Code2|whonix-…}} in the list, use the “View” menu to toggle the setting “Show/Hide inactive VMs”.

[[File:qubes-whonix3.png]]

[[File:qubes-whonix5.png]]

After finishing the download process , you should see {{Code2|whonix-ws}} and {{Code2|whonix-gw}}.

[[File:qubes-whonix2.png]]

'''4. Enable AppArmor''' '''(optional, testers-only security enhancement)'''
{{Qubes_AppArmor}}

'''5. Create Whonix-Gateway ProxyVM'''

<code>
Qubes VM Manager -> Create AppVM 
</code>

[[File:qubes-whonix4.png]]

Then change the settings as it shown below:- (you can choose any name&color you like)

[[File:Create_Qubes-Whonix-Gateway_ProxyVM23423.png]]

'''6. Create Whonix-Workstation AppVM'''

<code>
Qubes VM Manager -> Create AppVM 
</code>

[[File:Create_Qubes-Whonix-Workstation_AppVM2.png]]

'''7. TemplateVM proxy settings'''

a) Attach Whonix TemplateVMs to a Whonix-Gateway ProxyVM (commonly called sys-whonix)

<code>
Qubes VM Manager -> one left click on TemplateVM whonix-gw -> VM-Settings
</code>

[[File:whonix_templatevms_to_a_GW.png]]

<code>
NetVM: -> sys-whonix -> OK
</code>

[[File:Qubes-Whonix-Gateway_TemplateVM_Qubes_VM_Manager_Settings.png]]

b) Attach Whonix TemplateVMs to a Whonix-Workstation appVM (commonly called ws-whonix)

<code>
Qubes VM Manager -> one left click on TemplateVM whonix-ws -> VM-Settings
</code>

then

<code>
NetVM: -> sys-whonix -> OK
</code>

[[File:whonix_templatevms_to_a_GW2.png]]

'''8. start Whonix-Workstation AppVM'''

For example, start the [[Tor Browser|browser]].

<code>
Qubes App Launcher (blue/grey "Q") -> {{Code2|Domain: anon-whonix}} -> Privacy Browser
</code>

